How can I do business like this?

318
00:23:14,084 --> 00:23:14,876
Give it to him.

319
00:23:16,084 --> 00:23:17,334
He can drink however much he wants.

320
00:23:18,292 --> 00:23:19,792
He's had a lot today.

321
00:23:20,459 --> 00:23:21,251
Give it to him.

322
