Hey, man, I'm sorry.

325
00:23:38,334 --> 00:23:38,709
Sorry.

326
00:23:41,209 --> 00:23:41,917
Mom,

327
00:23:42,834 --> 00:23:44,667
before I was born,

328
00:23:44,959 --> 00:23:46,334
