351
00:25:46,917 --> 00:25:47,751
Come talk to me.

352
00:25:50,709 --> 00:25:51,501
What's wrong?

353
00:25:52,334 --> 00:25:53,209
You in a bad mood?

354
00:25:56,167 --> 00:25:56,959
A little bit.

355
00:25:58,959 --> 00:25:59,876
Let's play a game.

356
00:26:00,501 --> 00:26:02,001
