she wants to live her life.

478
00:40:07,001 --> 00:40:08,001
I have an idea.

479
00:40:19,501 --> 00:40:21,876
A pair of hands beyond repair and beautification,

480
00:40:22,209 --> 00:40:24,376
Warmth is always behind,

481
