517
00:43:11,417 --> 00:43:12,167
Which one of you is Lv Xia?

518
00:43:13,292 --> 00:43:14,084
Sign this.

519
00:43:17,167 --> 00:43:17,959
This is for you.

520
00:43:20,001 --> 00:43:21,292
(Lv Xia, your situation with the police
