885
01:07:40,084 --> 01:07:42,542
it means your mom died for something.

886
01:07:45,917 --> 01:07:50,376
"On this busy intersection,

887
01:07:51,751 --> 01:07:56,459
standing in the rain,

888
01:07:57,626 --> 01:08:02,917
